title: Receiving Yards or Deceiving Yards? Week 3 Waiver Pickups I The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck run through the fantasy implications of Drew Brees and Ben Roethlisberger’s injuries (02:00), whether Lamar Jackson, Austin Ekeler, and John Ross’s stats are real or fake (26:15), and Daniel Jones coming for Eli Manning’s job (37:00).
